News.Title: Remus Pharmaceuticals Reports 34% Jump in H1 Net Profit to 175M Rupees
News.Summary: Remus Pharmaceuticals reported H1 consolidated net profit of 175 million rupees compared to 131 million rupees in the same period last year. Revenue increased to 4 billion rupees from 2.72 billion rupees year-over-year. EBITDA rose to 269 million rupees from 211 million rupees, though EBITDA margin declined to 6.7% from 7.8% in the previous year.
